name: Kaguya / Kaguya Ōtsutsuki (大筒木カグヤ) / [Naruto: Shippuden]
description:
Kaguya Ōtsutsuki / The Rabbit Goddess

Trained on 130 images with the resolution of 768x768. Suggested Lora strength 0.7~ 1. I feel like kaguya is pretty complex to train unlike the rest of the cast. I did the best i could to make her look good. Feel free to drop some feedback if you don't mind.

There are two type of variants skin tone. You'll get the natural skin colour if you don't add the tag pale skin. Adding pale skin tag will give you the white skin colour. The strength or whiteness intensity of pale skin colour can be can be controlled with increasing or decreasing the LORA strength or by increasing the weight of the pale skin tag.

Example : (pale skin:1.4)

For the rinne sharingan, i used the tag third eye and if the eye is closed use the forehead mark tag. Be warned it'll not always work due to the low dataset.

For the original kimono outfit use the tag otsutsuki kimono
For the hair length i would say you can add long hair or absurdly long hair.


If you want to generate very stylized shots of her use tags like night, red moon, cloudy sky,floating hair

Here is the basic prompt : masterpiece,best quality,kaguya, 1girl, solo, long hair, absurdly long hair, white short eyebrows, third eye, pale skin, horns, looking at viewer, otsutsuki kimono, cowboy shot,outdoors, moon
